    },
    {
      "content": "To reduce the risk of injury:",
      "pos": [
        2824,
        2853
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "A fully configured enclosure can weigh up to 32 kg (70 lbs); do not try to lift it by yourself.",
      "pos": [
        2857,
        2952
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Before moving the enclosure, always ensure that two people are available to handle the weight.",
      "pos": [
        2955,
        3049
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Be aware that one person attempting to lift this weight can sustain injuries.",
      "pos": [
        3050,
        3127
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Do not lift the enclosure by the handles on the Power and Cooling Modules (PCMs) located at the rear of the unit.",
      "pos": [
        3130,
        3243
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "These are not designed to take the weight.",
      "pos": [
        3244,
        3286
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Connection precautions",
      "pos": [
        3291,
        3313
      ]
    },
    {
      "pos": [
        3315,
        3448
      ],
      "content": "<ph id=\"ph1\">![</ph>Warning Icon<ph id=\"ph2\">](./media/storsimple-safety/IC740879.png)</ph> <ph id=\"ph3\">![</ph>Electrical Shock Icon<ph id=\"ph4\">](./media/storsimple-safety/IC740882.png)</ph> <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>WARNING!<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept>"
    },
    {
      "content": "To reduce the likelihood of injury, electrical shock, or death:",
      "pos": [
        3450,
        3513
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "When powered by multiple AC sources, disconnect all supply power for complete isolation.",
      "pos": [
        3517,
        3605
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Permanently unplug the unit before you move it or if you think it has become damaged in any way.",
      "pos": [
        3609,
        3705
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Provide a safe electrical earth connection to the power supply cords.",
      "pos": [
        3709,
        3778
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Verify that the grounding of the enclosure meets the national and local requirements before applying power.",
      "pos": [
        3779,
        3886
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Ensure that the power connection is always disconnected prior to the removal of a PCM from the enclosure.",
      "pos": [
        3890,
        3995
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Given that the plug on the power supply cord is the main disconnect device, ensure that the socket outlets are located near the equipment and are easily accessible.",
      "pos": [
        3999,
        4163
      ]
    },
    {
      "pos": [
