        7250,
        7372
      ]
    },
    {
      "pos": [
        7374,
        7440
      ],
      "content": "<ph id=\"ph1\">![</ph>Notice Icon<ph id=\"ph2\">](./media/storsimple-safety/IC740881.png)</ph> <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>NOTICE:<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept>"
    },
    {
      "content": "For the proper cooling of your rack system:",
      "pos": [
        7442,
        7485
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Ensure that the rack design takes into consideration the maximum enclosure operating ambient temperature of 35 degrees Celsius (95 degrees Fahrenheit).",
